<template>
  <v-main class="bg-grey-lighten-3">
    <v-container>
      <post-list
          :posts="post"
      />
    </v-container>
  </v-main>






</template>

<script>
import {mapActions, mapGetters, mapState} from "vuex";
import PostList from "@/components/layouts/PostList.vue";



 export default {
   components:{PostList},
  mounted() {
    this.fetchPost();

  },
  computed:{
      // productId(){
      //   return +this.$route.params.id;
      // },
    ...mapGetters({
      post:'post',
    }),
    ...mapState({
      setPost:state => state.post.post,
    })
  },
  methods:{
    ...mapActions({
      fetchPost:'fetchPost',
    }),
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>

</style>
